also called the Bell triangle or the Peirce triangle,
OEIS [A011971](https://oeis.org/A011971):

```
>>> 0:6.triangularArray { :n :k |
>>> 	0:k.sum { :i |
>>> 		binomial(k, i)
>>> 		*
>>> 		bellNumber(n - k + i)
>>> 	}
>>> }
[
	1;
	1 2;
	2 3 5;
	5 7 10 15;
	15 20 27 37 52;
	52 67 87 114 151 203;
	203 255 322 409 523 674 877
]
```

